            <p props="electron">When the audio and video stream recording state changes, the SDK triggers this callback to report the current recording state and the reason for the change.</p>
            <p props="rn">When the recording state of an audio or video stream changes, the SDK triggers this callback to report the current recording state and the reason for the change.</p>
